Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_pwr_net(25.10)                                        init_pwr_net(25.10)

Name
       init_pwr_net

Syntax
         init_pwr_net <list_of_power_nets>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies the list of global power nets used in the design. This global
       variable  replaces the previous rda_Input(ui_pwrnet) configuration file
       variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies VDD as the power  net  in  the
                design.

                set init_pwr_net {VDD}

Related Information
              * init_design

